xwikidoc.title: How do I export the patient database as JSON

property.answer:
You can export several patient records in one JSON file from the //Browse All Data// page, filtering which records to export and which fields to include in the output.
The //Browse All Data// page can be found at the top right of the page:
[[image:all_data.png]]
The //Export database as JSON// option is then found here on the //Browse All Data// page:
[[image:export_all_JSON.png]]
=== Additional Resources ===
If you're interested in a programmable way of getting data out, see [[the Integration page of the Administration guide>>AdminGuide.Integration]].
